name: Individual Kaleido 07
description:
Individual Kaleido 07 with a seed based on the viewer's tezos-address, renders differently for everyone.
If you own the OBJKT, Click/Tap to switch to alternate figure.

Uses the hicdex API and therefore depends on it. This is all experimental and might break in the future. OBJKT uses p5js with p5.collide, p5.createloop and post5.
- @TeNinEightNFTs
